data.lean: lemma pow_add (a m n : mynat) : a ^ (m + n) = a ^ m * a ^ n :=
data.editorText:
induction n with n hn,
  rw pow_zero a,
  rw mul_one (a ^ m),
  rw add_zero m,
  refl,
  rw add_succ m n,
  rw pow_succ a (m + n),
  rw pow_succ a n,
  rw hn,
  rw mul_assoc,
  refl,

data.lean: lemma mul_pow (a b n : mynat) : (a * b) ^ n = a ^ n * b ^ n :=
data.editorText:
induction n with n hn,
  rw pow_zero (a * b),
  rw pow_zero a,
  rw pow_zero b,
  rw mul_one,
  refl,
  rw pow_succ (a * b) n,
  rw hn,
  rw mul_left_comm,
  rw pow_succ a,
  rw pow_succ b,
  rw mul_comm (a ^ n) a,
  rw mul_assoc,
  rw mul_assoc,
  refl,

data.lean: lemma pow_pow (a m n : mynat) : (a ^ m) ^ n = a ^ (m * n) :=
data.editorText:
induction m with m hm, 
  rw pow_zero a,
  rw one_pow n,
  rw zero_mul n,
  rw pow_zero a,
  refl,
  rw pow_succ a m,
  rw mul_pow (a ^ m) a,
  rw hm,
  rw succ_mul m n,
  rw pow_add a (m * n) n,
  refl,

lemma add_squared (a b : mynat) :
  (a + b) ^ (2 : mynat) = a ^ (2 : mynat) + b ^ (2 : mynat) + 2 * a * b :=
data.editorText:
rw two_eq_succ_one,
rw one_eq_succ_zero,
repeat {rw pow_succ},
rw pow_zero (a + b),
rw pow_zero a,
rw pow_zero b,
rw succ_mul,
rw succ_mul,
rw zero_mul a,
rw zero_add a,
rw one_mul (a + b),
rw one_mul a,
rw one_mul b,
rw mul_add,
rw add_mul,
rw add_mul,
rw add_mul,
rw add_comm (a * b) (b * b),
rw add_assoc,
rw add_comm (b * a) ((b*b)+(a*b)),
rw add_assoc,
rw add_assoc,
rw mul_comm b a,
refl,
